{"tid":2454068,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁愛詩 : 單憑一人一票選舉制度，不一定代表公平","createTime":"2021-03-20T02:59:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T07:29:23.000Z","uid":350584,"like":8,"dislike":140,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"434daf40dc00205850358effeb924744f3f8b34b","tid":2454068,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T02:59:58.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】基本法委員會前副主任梁愛詩表示，修改香港選舉制度目的是防止損害香港國家利益的人取得特區行政及立法權，她指單憑一人一票的選舉制度不一定代表公平。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=428108\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D428108&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDExj1a1M9JfR6d2dSWReNkw%3D&h=8cd558e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D428108&h=62633781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=428108</a>"},{"pid":"73f4ea6b47d94584a7907098a7653dfead67f398","tid":2454068,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":25,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T03:00:21.000Z","msg":"梁愛詩：「新的選舉委員會的組成，更能體現均衡參與和兼顧各階層利益的原則，上一屆區議會的選舉獲得57%選票的黨派，居然取得85%的議席，單憑一人一票的選舉是否必然達至公平的結果？在一國兩制處於變形、走樣的危機下，我們首先要回到正軌，才能發展一個符合香港實際情況的民主制度，那是民主的優化、不是退步。」"},{"pid":"5c123c648b7d10ce4d00338712af4e1cc82ad3dd","tid":2454068,"uid":125168,"like":115,"dislike":1,"score":114,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T03:01:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5aad1a75b50d59218650c183213e66967ec6612","tid":2454068,"uid":350584,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T03:01:55.000Z","msg":"新的選舉委員會的組成，更能體現均衡參與和兼顧各階層利益的原則，上一屆區議會的選舉獲得57%選票的黨派，居然取得85%的議席，單憑一人一票的選舉是否必然達至公平的結果？"},{"pid":"66744fac8e6d7ab89601fdf272d7b66dad4edc31","tid":2454068,"uid":393145,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T03:02:32.000Z","msg":"袋住先都係一人一票<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"